<body class="bg-white text-gray-900">
    <header class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 glass h-16 flex items-center">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                VKX Wallet
            </a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container mx-auto px-6 pt-32 pb-20 max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-8 tracking-tight">Privacy Policy</h1>
        
        <div class="prose prose-blue prose-sm md:prose-base text-gray-600 space-y-8">
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-widest">Last Updated: January 2026</p>
            
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
                <p>
                    VKX Wallet ("we", "us", or "our") provides a non-custodial wallet application. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information in connection with your use of our mobile application and website.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">2. Non-Custodial Nature</h2>
                <p>
                    VKX Wallet is a non-custodial application. This means we do not have access to your private keys, backup phrases (seed phrases), or the funds stored in your wallet. We cannot recover your account if you lose your backup phrase.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">3. Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
                <p>
                    Because VKX Wallet is designed to be private and decentralized, we do not collect:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4">
                    <li>Your name, email address (unless you contact support), or physical address.</li>
                    <li>Your IP address or device location.</li>
                    <li>Your private keys or backup phrases.</li>
                    <li>Your transaction history (which is publicly available on the blockchain but not linked to your identity by us).</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">4. Information We May Collect</h2>
                <p>
                    The only information we may receive is:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4">
                    <li><strong>Support Communications:</strong> If you contact us via email, we will have access to your email address and any information you provide to help resolve your issue.</li>
                    <li><strong>Public Blockchain Data:</strong> Our app interacts with public blockchains. Any transactions you make are public and recorded on those blockchains.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">5. Use of Information</h2>
                <p>
                    Any information we receive (like support emails) is used solely to respond to your requests or improve the technical functionality of the application. We do not sell or share your data with third parties for marketing purposes.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">6. Security</h2>
                <p>
                    Your security depends on you keeping your backup phrase safe. Since VKX Wallet is non-custodial, the primary responsibility for the security of your funds lies with you.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="pt-8 border-t border-gray-100">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
                <p>
                    If you have questions about this policy, contact us at: <a href="mailto:contato@vkxtech.com.br" class="text-blue-600 font-bold hover:underline">contato@vkxtech.com.br</a>
                </p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-100 py-12">
